Revision history for Perl extension Module::LocalBuild.

The contributors that suggested a given feature are shown in [].  [by ...]
indicates the contributor was also the author of the fix; Thanks!

* Module::LocalBuild 1.013 2010/08/04

****	Fix Pod::Usage dependency, rt51024.  [Andreas Koenig]

****	Give obvious error message when MS-Windows unsupported.

* Module::LocalBuild 1.012 2010/01/12

***	Ignore .git directories when detecting changes.

* Module::LocalBuild 1.011 2009/05/19

**	This package is now licensed under LGPL v3 and/or Artistic v2.0.

***	Ignore Make::Cache temporary files when detecting changes.

* Module::LocalBuild 1.010 2008/08/15

***	Add mlbuilder --makeflag option.

***	Add mlbuilder --version option.

* Module::LocalBuild 1.001 2007/05/07

****	Fix localboot test.  [cpan-testers]

* Module::LocalBuild 1.000 2007/05/03

**	First packaged release to CPAN.

* Module::LocalBuild 0.000 2001

**	First version created for internal use.

